@startuml
title **Dubbo 获取zk注册中心实例**

participant "RegistryProtocol" as RP
participant "AbstractRegistryFactory" as ARF
participant "ZookeeperRegistryFactory" as ZRF

RP -> ARF : **[01]** registryFactory.getRegistry(registryUrl)
ARF -> ZRF : **[02]** registry = createRegistry(url);
ZRF --> RP : **[03]** new ZookeeperRegistry(url, zookeeperTransporter);

@enduml
